@startuml component
title Nozzles Budget App — Component Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor User

package "src/" {
  [main.js\n(entrypoint)] as main
  [BudgetStore\n(pure logic)] as store
  [LocalStorage adapter\n(NullStorage in tests)] as storage
  [ui.js\n(DOM bindings)] as ui
}

database "Browser\nlocalStorage" as ls

User --> ui : clicks / forms
ui --> store : setBudget / addExpense\n/ removeExpense / updateExpense
store --> ui : subscribe(snapshot)
main --> store : new BudgetStore()
main --> storage : new LocalStorage(KEY)
main --> ui : mount({store})
store --> storage : subscribe → save(snapshot)
storage --> ls : setItem / getItem

note right of store
  No DOM access.
  Returns {ok, error?} from
  every mutation. Validation
  lives here.
end note

note right of ui
  No business rules.
  Just renders snapshots
  + dispatches store calls.
end note
@enduml
